<h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
<p>Dear <%= @user.name %>,</p>
<p>Thank you for your order! Your order number is <%= @order.id %>. Below are the details:</p>

<ul>
  <% @order_items.each do |item| %>
    <li><%= item.product_name %> - Quantity: <%= item.quantity %> - Price: <%= item.product_price %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>Total: <%= @order.total_price %></p>
<p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>

<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>Your E-Commerce Team</p>
